parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of airbags to deploy in the event of a crash can increase the risk of injury or fatality to vehicle occupants.
symptoms: Airbags do not deploy in a crash
airbag warning light stays on
airbag sensor failure.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: False airbag deployment can cause loss of control of the vehicle, leading to accidents and injuries.
symptoms: Airbag deploys unexpectedly
airbag deploys in a non-crash scenario
airbag sensor failure.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Malfunction of the airbag system can lead to false deployments, failure to deploy, or other issues that can compromise vehicle safety.
symptoms: Airbag warning light stays on
airbag sensor failure
dash and airbag seal coming apart.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The engine block defect can cause the engine to lose power, especially when turning corners or climbing hills, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle loses power when turning corners or climbing hills
the engine slows down almost to a stop
the engine light is illuminated
oil consumption/leakage
loud rattling noise from the catalytic converter.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The cracked exhaust pipe can cause exhaust fumes to enter the passenger cabin, which can lead to health risks and accidents.
symptoms: Exhaust fumes enter the passenger cabin
loud rattling noise from the exhaust system.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The engine failure can cause the vehicle to stall or lose power, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The engine dies or loses power
no acceleration
the engine light is illuminated
oil consumption/leakage.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The catalytic converter failure can cause a loud rattling noise, which can be a nuisance and potentially lead to further engine problems.
symptoms: Loud rattling noise from the catalytic converter.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The defective energy management loop in the seatbelt can cause the belt to malfunction, leading to injuries or fatalities in the event of an accident.
symptoms: The seatbelt tightens or locks up while riding
requiring removal to reset
or fails to release after locking without unbuckling.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The misrepresentation of seatbelt repair parts can lead to the installation of defective or outdated parts, compromising the safety of the vehicle occupants.
symptoms: The dealership installs an older or defective part instead of the updated part as represented
and refuses to correct the issue or provide a refund.
